Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep at my desk again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The light that pours down on this town,\Nthis country, shines on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On the place I've chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On the new feelings inside me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.81,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 3: Shining Time of Promise"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to see Prince Zen today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mitsuhide and Kiki asked me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I've been wondering about this for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but what was the object\Nhanging from that man's neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a piece of identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Identification...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone working at the castle has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not permitted to\Nenter the palace without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're fine, though, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard everything from the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and wait at the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Being friends with the prince and all--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki's so cool, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, do you have business with the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, but he is currently\Nwith someone else right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That person again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're beautiful no matter when I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She has nothing to prove her social standing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That red-haired girl claiming\Nto be the prince's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a vulgar color...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We called you here today to help out with Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After being out of the castle\Non official business the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he snuck out to observe the local area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He snuck out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he always does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, it made him late returning\Nto the castle without permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ministers around him seemed to\Ncome down hard on him about it afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Zen depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He decided to show his\Ncontriteness with his actions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and shut himself up in his office,\Nworking without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say anything yet,\Nbut it's really me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, Kiki and I asked Shirayuki to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"If I have time to sleep,\Nthen I wanna see Shirayuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you guys\Nkept bugging me about sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you start writing\N"Shirayuki" all over your documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you spend some time with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be a symptom of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Before all your replies become\N"Shirayuki," you should spend--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, we need to talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Should I go home for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for interrupti--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't being fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry they made you come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Looks like you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when\NI'm away from the castle for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll become a\Nprince in name only one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you're overworking yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished twice as much as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give them anything to\Ncomplain about the next time I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind deskwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it's easy to lose sight\Nof what's going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The country, Clarines,\Nspreads out past the castle walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, your country is great, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Zen--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to sleep a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stay here until Mitsuhide comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen is constantly fighting even\Nas he lives as this country's prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to work hard toward my own goal, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So that red-haired girl\Nis Prince Zen's friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, are you done sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide saw her off, and she went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl must've forgotten this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, please excuse me\Nfor interrupting your rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Lord Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't meet up with people\Nfrom the outside so carelessly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't forget your position\Nas this country's prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must carefully choose\Nwhom you become close with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to protect myself,\Nand my authority, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then stop inviting that\Ntown girl of unknown lineage into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl will have expectations\Nand take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she asks for social status\Nappropriate for her position,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or asks you to introduce her to the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if she\Nasks you for selfish things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Submitting quickly to the strong, and never\Ntrying to advance with her own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping a girl like that by your side\Nwill only draw criticism from your retainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to gain from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Never trying to advance\Nwith her own power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, what if it's a girl\Nwithout those expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness, where would\Nyou find a girl like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking if it would\Nbe all right if there was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're saying such a girl exists,\Nthen I would definitely like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see her, Lord Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness! I did not come\Nto engage in wordplay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't play for me, either, Lord Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that you will open your eyes\Nto the truth as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a change of scenery.\NI'm going to get some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, that prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can say to change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no choice but to\Nspeak directly to the girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, shall I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like the shironagi herb, but the\Nshape of the leaves is a little different...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the encyclopedia said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I forget it at Zen's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Shirayuki pass from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki has permission to pass\Nas Prince Zen's personal guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an order from the prince:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Regarding the treatment of Shirayuki,\Nbecause of the criticism of my retainers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,she shall hereafter no longer\Nhave permission to enter the palace."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand the\Nprince's agonizing decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you must tell the prince\Nthat we just allowed Shirayuki to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she left her book in the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she's with the prince...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's being criticized?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But was the order just now really from Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave the castle today,\NI won't be able to come back to see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens to Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hear this directly from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You over there, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That red hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that you are the prince's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for stopping you suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. No problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew... At least, I thought I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That I could only see Zen because of his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming for a path that allows me to be in\Nthe same place as him through my own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I can--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Red-haired guest, do not\Ntake another step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...telling me not to go near Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There is someone in this castle who will not\Nallow Zen and I to be in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,... Zen is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not gonna run away from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is taking a roundabout way\Nto get to the prince's rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it's convenient for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go home, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my book...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, did someone talk to you before this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's that arrow in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone shot at you inside the castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, why didn't you call the soldiers then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... But Zen, before you\Nget angry, hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not be angry about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so unconcerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to stop\Ncoming here without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is someone who doesn't\Nwant the two of us to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have to try confronting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm by myself, then the\Nother person might try to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Zen!\N--That's what I'd like to say, but all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If the other person won't leave you alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,make them stop even\Nif you have to use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It could also be the\Nwork of more than one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I find them, I'll keep watch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you know who it is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident, so I won't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I make enemies easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I saw\NZen talking with his face downcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return to my residence,\Nso I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Confidence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How will I be able to figure out who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in the service of the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get into the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the Poet's Gate,\Nwith permission from a certain personage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to see him now, so if you\Ndoubt me, would you like to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I have found an intruder,\NI cannot allow them to go any further than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have you leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One must have authority in order to\Ninvite those from the outside into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not look like you have the social status\Nto be invited by one with such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is saying this with certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is as you say, and I should not be here,\Nthen stop me with your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't actually ask him,\Nbut it was enough just to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"She shall hereafter no longer\Nhave permission to enter the palace."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were not Zen's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Never trying to advance\Nwith her own power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't play for me, either, Lord Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about an\Norder purported to be from Prince Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you wouldn't\Nbe scared off by a little arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like I can\Nrun away, either, so I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That order and the arrow with\Nthe threat on it were all my doing, not his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did these myself thinking of the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for help from\Nsomeone of humble birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A lord with a strange sense of pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say it was for me, Lord Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the wrong way to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on the outcome,\Nit could have caused an uproar in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you listening the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I found the marquess,\Nand he started talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just say, I had to use all\Nmy self-control not to come out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At least forgive me for eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good answer, Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl! How can you call the prince by his name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Lord Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's bad to have\Npeople around who value authority
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and social status over everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe it is necessary as a\Nprince to understand different perspectives,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like those of you and Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Haruka, is your title important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please treat it with importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This will not happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Case closed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Obi, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling "Master"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm going to\Nkeep you where I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so wary.\NI won't lift another finger against that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'd believe you so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it! I like her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, she looks like\Nshe'll be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going overboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Mitsuhide! Do something about that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go anywhere with a pretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "you." Call me "Obi."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there shouldn't be any\Nproblems if we leave it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I make enemies easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Application information?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to apply for this, so I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... for this castle's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to one day be able to go through\Nthe gates by myself and come be your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone I want to\Ntreasure my time together with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can become his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait, too, in this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what pushes me from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and is my guidepost for moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the chief herbalist, Garak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to take\Nyour test, right? Are you calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm a kid. It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're locked in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.50,0:24:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look for the sake of your resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:20.01,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 4: From the Small Hand,\Na Burgeoning Concerto Resonates"
